data.description: This beautifully designed home offers both comfort and versatility. The main level includes the master bedroom, complete with an extra room that's perfect for a nursery, home office, or fitness area. Four additional bedrooms, with one currently serving as a home office. Upstairs, a unique space that includes a second living area, bedroom, and full bath, offering ideal privacy for guests or a superb in-law suite. Outside, the property has a stunning pool and a covered patio, perfect for relaxation and outdoor gatherings. The home is topped with a long-lasting metal roof and constructed with CBS. Located in a sought-after neighborhood, this home combines tranquility with the ease of access to all. This home combines tranquility with the ease of access to all the necessary amenities.
